results.title: Stay Alive! Conclusion
results.description: Alpha Flight shows up to help Wolvie put down a Wendigo powered Mauvais.

results.title: The Logan Files Part 1
results.description: Lady Deathstrike and Omega Red begin to take down all of Wolverine's close friends; Before Wolvie can respond, his powers are taken away by a mysterious blast from the Weapon X project.

results.title: Laying the Groundwork
results.description: Sasquatch learns that the Hudson's plan has gone down and leaves a wounded Aurora to go and find them; Aurora is captured and brought to Weapon X.

results.title: The Logan Files Part 2
results.description: A powerless Wolvie must take on two of his most fearsome foes to save the life of his adopted daughter.

results.title: The Logan Files Conclusion
results.description: Wolverine rescues Amiko from a trio of his baddest bad guys; Wolvie fights Sabretooth through the original Weapon X compound trying to obtain the Logan Files--a computer program that contains his true history and origin; As Sabretooth escapes and Weapon X soldiers rush in, Logan keels over and is pronounced dead.

results.title: The Vow
results.description: On the anniversary of Mariko's death, Matsuo is about to commit hari kari rather than have Wolverine show up and slice off another piece of anatomy; But the ritual is halted when the recently deceased Logan never comes.

results.title: The Logan Files Epilogue
results.description: After being killed last issue, Wolvie is guided through an afterlife of memories by an old love and winds up fighting a band of dead enemies with his recently deceased pal, Colossus.

results.title: The Shadow Pulpit Book 1
results.description: Wolvie is approached by a priest and told of a nefarious plot by a shadow segment of the Office of the Inquisition bent on controlling people's minds.

results.title: The Shadow Pulpit Book 2
results.description: Logan takes on the Vatican to try and rescue a captured priest.

results.title: Of Lesser Demons...
results.description: Shaman enlists Wolvie's help in freeing Alpha Flight from the clutches of a shaman turned evil earth spirit.

results.title: All At Sea
results.description: Wolverine tries to save Roughouse from the clutches of Geist but fails.

results.title: Everything's Zen
results.description: Wolverine guides one of Shaman's students through a rite of passage.

results.title: Down the Road
results.description: Wolvie takes the final pickup ride with a hard-drinking, killer hillbilly.

results.title: Good Cop/Bad Cop Part One
results.description: A down on his luck cop is trying to bring a dirty officer to justice when their paths cross Wolverine.

results.title: Good Cop/Bad Cop Part 2
results.description: Wolvie helps a down on his luck cop take down a dirty player on the force.

results.title: Heroes and Villains
results.description: Tiger Shark is hired to take on Wolverine; On the trail of Roughouse, Wolvie stumbles across a revolution in Tierra Verde.

results.title: Possession Is The Law
results.description: Jessica is possessed by the Black Blade which makes it really tough for Wolvie and the Silver Samurai to take it from her; Wolvie succeeds and is taken over by the Sword.

results.title: Miracles
results.description: Wolvie tussles with Tiger Shark; Roughouse is freed but has been injected with drugs that are killing him.

results.title: Outburst!
results.description: Caridad is transformed into Spore and Wolvie has to take him down.

results.title: Endings
results.description: After the battle with Spore, Wolvie heads back to Madripoor; Magneto has a little talk with Geist.

results.title: Snow Blind
results.description: Wolvie helps a street kid who has stolen a bomb from the Assassin who is trying to get it back.

results.title: Heir Aid
results.description: Wolverine tells Gabriel a bedtime story of a boy raised by Wolverines.

results.title: Memory of Peace
results.description: Wolvie recovers a valuable family heirloom of an old friend who was killed because of it.

results.title: The Lazarus Project Part 1: Predators and Prey!
results.description: Jess gets beat up in a fight with a Robot and she and Lindsay return to the USA.

results.title: The Lazarus Project Part 2: The Stranger
The Lazarus Project Part 3: The Road Back
The Black Blade
results.description: Lindsay and Silver Samurai try to save Jessica from a possessed Wolverine; The Samurai ends up with the Sword.

results.title: The Lazarus Project Part 4: Family Matters
Against the Blade of the Yakuza
Grave Undertakings
results.description: Buried Alive!

results.title: The Hunter in Darkness
results.description: Wolvie helps an old mountie track down a killer who has kidnapped a young girl, but the Hunter in Darkness is also on their trail; As Doolin is dying, he remembers Logan from two encounters in his distant past.

results.title: Blood Sand and Claws!
results.description: Through an indirect wish of Lady Deathstrike's, Gateway sends she, Wolverine and Puck back to 1937 Spain to hang out with Ernest Hemingway.

results.title: ...It Tolls For Thee
results.description: Wolvie and Puck land in 1937 in the middle of the Battle of Guernica with Lady Deathstrike hot on their trail.

results.title: Fall Back and Spring Forward
results.description: Wolvie and Deathstrike wage war across the ages as the time storm whips them through their past and dumps them in the present; Pierce comes close to completing his robotic duo who are to take down Wolverine.

results.title: See Venice & Die!
results.description: Storm searches for Logan after she finds the mob has been issuing wanted posters because someone who looks just like her fellow X-Man has been knocking over their operations; Elsie Dee (who is smarter than Pierce thinks she is) modifies herself and Albert; Wolvie tracks down his robot double and rips through the impersonator; Elsie Dee prepares to fulfill her programming by blowing up Wolverine.

results.title: Deconstruction
results.description: Elsie Dee lures Wolverine into Pierce's explosive trap, but finds that she cannot blow up the hero who saved her robotic life; Albert falls in with some mob goons and gets mowed down by police.
